tment-bank-joins-chorus-experts-calls-fiscal-stimulus-intensify?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在最近的一份研究报告中，中国国际金融公司确定直接财政刺激是今年经济增长的最佳行动方案，此前几轮对企业的信贷支持并未收到预期效果。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253261/chinese-investment-bank-joins-chorus-experts-calls-fiscal-stimulus-intensify?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京表示，中国在南海闪点设置浮动屏障是“必要的”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253276/chinese-floating-barrier-south-china-sea-flashpoint-was-necessary-beijing-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>外交部证实在有争议的黄岩岛设立屏障是为了“维护主权”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253276/chinese-floating-barrier-south-china-sea-flashpoint-was-necessary-beijing-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>国民党副主席夏安德开始中国大陆之行，呼吁与台湾对话</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253252/kmt-deputy-chief-andrew-hsia-starts-mainland-china-trip-call-dialogue-taiwan?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>夏说，他没有计划会见大陆官员，但对这种可能性持开放态度，并对金门附近两名大陆渔民的死亡表示哀悼</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253252/kmt-deputy-chief-andrew-hsia-starts-mainland-china-trip-call-dialogue-taiwan?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>C919和空客工厂推动的中国航空业的繁荣是韩国企业“必须抓住”的机会</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3253251/chinas-aviation-boon-driven-c919-and-airbus-plant-opportunity-south-korean-firms-must-pursue?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>韩国国家贸易和投资促进机构表示，中国正在将航空零部件供应链从北美和欧洲转移到邻国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3253251/chinas-aviation-boon-driven-c919-and-airbus-plant-opportunity-south-korean-firms-must-pursue?utm_so