 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253236/chinas-top-corruption-watchdog-puts-belt-and-road-projects-rural-strategy-cross-hairs?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国抨击美国在世贸组织评估中的“抹黑策略”，称华盛顿掩盖其“破坏行为”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253231/china-slams-us-smear-tactics-wto-assessment-says-washington-covering-its-sabotage?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>自中美贸易战爆发以来，华盛顿关于中国遵守世贸组织情况的报告继续指责中国，而北京则表示美国正在转移人们对其自身“违反和破坏世贸组织”行为的注意力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 08:42:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253231/china-slams-us-smear-tactics-wto-assessment-says-washington-covering-its-sabotage?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>西方国家警告要求供应，中国正在应对冬季风暴停电</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253228/china-beating-winter-storm-power-blackouts-western-countries-warn-get-supplies?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>2008 年重大电网崩溃后，宝贵的经验教训现在帮助我们在大风暴期间保持供电。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 08:37:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253228/china-beating-winter-storm-power-blackouts-western-countries-warn-get-supplies?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>华为云部门依靠蓬勃发展的人工智能需求，在欧洲和中东拓展全球业务</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253185/huaweis-cloud-unit-banks-booming-ai-demand-global-footprint-expansion-europe-and-middle-east?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>华为将于三月份将云服务扩展到埃及，并将很快在香港开设人工智能云计算中心，这是华为在中国大陆以外的首个中心。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 06:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253185/huaweis-cloud-unit-banks-booming-ai-demand-global-footprint-expansion-europe-and-middle-east?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国警惕寒冷天气对春季蔬菜作物的损害</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253143/china-alert-cold-weather-damage-s